### 5. Agent Quality

- **Claude (Opus + Sonnet)**: Best overall code quality. Clean architecture, proper error handling, comprehensive test coverage. Minor issues: duplicate issue filing, weak-key API edge case.
- **Codex**: Good contributor (195 tasks closed) but carries most protocol/architecture drift findings historically (27 protocol errors, 21 architecture drift, 34 security issues). This review found 1 new correctness issue.
- **Cursor**: Lowest volume (31 tasks) and highest bug rate (0.29). No new findings this review but historically the weakest.

